00:11:38.340 --> 00:11:41.020
times x, which is
almost momentum again.

00:11:41.020 --> 00:11:42.700
We need a velocity
and not a position,

00:11:42.700 --> 00:11:44.020
but we have 1 over time.

00:11:44.020 --> 00:11:48.570
So if we take h bar
