01:16:10.100 --> 01:16:11.400
and an extremely efficient
way to write down

01:16:11.400 --> 01:16:12.752
the Hermite polynomials.

01:16:12.752 --> 01:16:14.460
They're the things
that you get by acting

01:16:14.460 --> 01:16:18.920
on this with this operator
